      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以第一个节点是提案本身。接下来是不是要分叉？我记得你们有两种签名模式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sig_mode",
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，一个是链式签名（chain），维护者在完全相同的代码树上共同签名提交；另一个是见证模式（attestation），他们在树OID和上下文上添加.sig文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "chain",
        "attestation",
        "C",
        "D",
        "Maintainers co-sign commits over identical tree",
        "Maintainers add .sig files over tree OID + context"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在B节点画了一个判断框标注sig_mode，然后分出两条路径到C和D。两种模式最后是不是要汇合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，无论哪种方式，最后都要检查阈值是否满足。这个判断节点很关键，叫threshold met。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "threshold met?",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果阈值没满足，直接拒绝？我画一个Reject的终止节点G。",
